    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "ふむふむ、今後きそうな高配当株は……\nただしアメリカの債券市場の流れによっては……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm-hmm‚ high-dividend stocks are likely to rise in the future…\nHowever‚ depending on the trends in the US bond market…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2599.9999999999995
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6166.6666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9649.999999999998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "悩ましいわ……具体的な銘柄は落ち着いて決めましょう\n店員さんすみませーん、コーヒーのおかわりください",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Considering… Let's decide on specific sectors carefully\nExcuse meー‚ Can I please have a refill of coffee?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5666666031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.56667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.5333332698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "店員さん！　私にはこちらのハニーポテトチップス\nパフェとココアをいただけますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me! Can I get a honey potato chop\nparfait and cocoa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.5333332698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "ん……？　ああっ！　あんた月ストの！\nなに勝手に私のテーブルに着いてるのよ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh…..? Ahh! You‚ the Moon Tempest!\nWhy are you sitting at my table so naturally!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.0333332698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.26667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私だって本意ではありませんわ！\n他に座席が空いてなかったんですもの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I‚ I didn't mean to do it either!\nThere were no other seats available!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.7999999364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "だとしても普通一声かけるでしょ！\nなんで黙って座んのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even so‚ you usually have to speak first!\nWhy are you sitting here quietly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.9999999364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.4666666031
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "真剣な表情でスマホを見つめていらしたので……\n邪魔したら悪いと思ったんですの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were looking at your smartphone with a serious face…\nI thought it would be bad to get in the way…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.4666666031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はぁ、もういいわ。ただし今、物凄く",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ha‚ that's fine. But right now‚ it's a",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.4999999364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.4999999364
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "大事なところだから、邪魔はしないでよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "very important situation‚ so don't get in my way",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もちろん！　任せてくださいまし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course! Leave it to me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.4999999364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.4999999364
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "成宮家の名に誓って、大人しくしてますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I swear on the name of the Narimiya family‚ I'll behave myself",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ふぅ……、銘柄も決まったし、そろそろ帰ろうかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew…‚ now that I've decided on the sectors‚ let’s get back to it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.6333347957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "すず……？　顔色が悪いけどお腹でも壊した？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu…? You look pale‚ you have a stomachache?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あの、franさん……その……バッグに\n入れてきたはずのお財布が……見当たらないんですの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "E-Excuse me‚ fran-san… Well…\nwallet that I clearly put in my bag… is nowhere to be seen!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1000014623,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "寮に忘れてきたんじゃないの？　食い逃げしたら\n捕まるわよ。お店の人に謝って後で払いに来なさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe you left it at the dorm? If you dine and dash‚\nI'll catch you. Apologize to the staff and come back later to pay",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.9000014623,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "どどどどどうしましょう……そんなことしたら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-w-w-w-what should I do… if I do that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.066668129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.066668129
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "成宮家も月ストも笑いものにされてしまいますわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Narimiya family and Moon Tempest become a laughingstock…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ぷっ……あはははっ……考え過ぎよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pfft… Ahahaha… you're overthinking it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.666668129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.666668129
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ私はお先に失礼するわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I'll be going first",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.2332969482
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "franさん待ってくださいまし！　私はどうすれば\nいいんですの？　一人にしないでくださいまし～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "fran-san‚ please wait! What should\nI do? Please don't leave me alone~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.2333317439,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7066.665204300009
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと静かに！　周りの人に気付かれる……\nって、もう気付かれてんじゃん、これ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just be quiet! People around you will notice…\nEven if I say that‚ it would have already been noticed‚ it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.5999984105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.5999984105
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.1999969482
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ささ、とりあえず、もう一度席に座ってくださいまし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ for now‚ please take a seat again!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.1999984105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "今後の対応を一緒に考えましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's think about how to respond next!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.8333302815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.9999984105
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kor_01_02-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、こんなガキんちょがお金に困ってるのに\n見捨てて出て行った、なんて思われたら炎上ものよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ughー‚ this little kid is worried about money\nIf people though I just passed‚ it would be a big issue",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.9999984105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "でも、突然私の向かいに座ってきたコイツに奢るのも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ I feel a bit angry buying it for the guy who suddenly sat",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.9666650772,
      "sfxList": []
